(7691, 'Magnisol 0.5gm/5ml 6 amps', 'ماجنيسول 0.5جم/5مل 6 امبولات', '45', '66', 'Magnesium sulphate', 'Memphis', 'Amp', 'أمبول', '', 'Magnesium supplements', '0.5gm', 'Used for immediate control of life-threatening convulsions in the treatment of severe toxemias (pre-eclampsia and eclampsia) of pregnancy and in the treatment of acute nephritis in children. Also indicated for replacement therapy in magnesium deficiency, especially in acute hypomagnesemia accompanied by signs of tetany similar to those of hypocalcemia. Also used in uterine tetany as a myometriat relaxant.', '6221050010830', '', 1820, '2024-07-29', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
